{"id": "art-1522", "label": "Art. 1522", "title": "Art. 1522", "slug": "art-1522", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1301220845\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1216\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1301220845\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 152<sup>2</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_767135291\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1215\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_767135291\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Salariatul are dreptul de a absenta de la locul de\nmunc&#259; în situa&#355;ii neprev&#259;zute, determinate de o situa&#355;ie de\nurgen&#355;&#259; familial&#259; cauzat&#259; de boal&#259; sau de accident,\ncare fac indispensabil&#259; prezen&#355;a imediat&#259; a salariatului, în\ncondi&#355;iile inform&#259;rii prealabile a angajatorului &#351;i cu\nrecuperarea perioadei absentate pân&#259; la acoperirea integral&#259; a\nduratei normale a programului de lucru a salariatului.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_849891352\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1214\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_849891352\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Absentarea de la locul de munc&#259; prev&#259;zut&#259;\nla alin. (1) nu poate avea o durat&#259; mai mare de 10 zile lucr&#259;toare\nîntr-un an calendaristic.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_144855337\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1213\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_144855337\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Angajatorul &#351;i salariatul stabilesc de comun acord\nmodalitatea de recuperare a perioadei de absen&#355;&#259;, precizat&#259; la\nalin. (1), în limita num&#259;rului de zile prev&#259;zute la alin. (2).</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}